\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\left.\mathcal{L}_{X}Y\right|_{p} & :=\lim_{t\rightarrow0}\frac{1}{t}\left(\left(d\left(\theta_{t}\right)_{p}\right)^{-1}\left(Y_{\theta_{t}(p)}\right)-Y_{p}\right)\nonumber \\
 & =\lim_{t\rightarrow0}\frac{1}{t}\left(d\left(\theta_{-t}\right)_{\theta_{t}(p)}\left(Y_{\theta_{t}(p)}\right)-Y_{p}\right),\label{eq:11}
\end{align}

\end_inset

其中，第二个方程来自事实：
\begin_inset Formula $\theta_{t}^{-1}=\theta_{-t}$
